verbose_text: Intriguingly, a certain number of specific areas never showed claudin 5a expression (15 of 16 larvae, three biological independent experiments, XREF_FIG G) : the primordial midbrain channels (PMBC), choroidal vascular plexus (CVP) (XREF_FIG G, arrows), anterior cerebral vein frontally located (ACeV) (XREF_FIG I-K), and at the location of the midbrain the dorsal midline junction (DMJ) and dorsal longitudinal vein (DLV) (XREF_FIG L-N).
